---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
---

<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
  <!-- Level 1 -->
  <div class="fun-card border-4 border-blue-400 border-opacity-30 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50 relative overflow-hidden group">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 text-8xl opacity-10 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-500">
      ⭐
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3 animate-bounce-slow">⭐</div>
      
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
        Level 1: 11 years +
      </h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-2xl">⏰</span>
          <span class="font-semibold">3 Hours per day</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-2xl">💰</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-orange-500 text-xl">€215 for 1 week</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        This course is aimed at young boys and girls tailored to their needs to encourage confidence in the kitchen. Students learn how to weigh and measure and why this is important. Students will learn how to prepare, cook and serve 2 dishes each day both savoury and sweet which they take home. 🍝🍰
      </p>
      
      <a href="#contact" class="mt-6 w-full block text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-pink-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg">
        Book Now! 🚀
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Level 2 -->
  <div class="fun-card border-4 border-pink-400 border-opacity-30 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-pink-50 relative overflow-hidden group">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 text-8xl opacity-10 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-500">
      🌟
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3 animate-bounce-slow">🌟</div>
      
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
        Level 2
      </h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-2xl">⏰</span>
          <span class="font-semibold">3 Hours per day</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-2xl">💰</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-orange-500 text-xl">€215 for 1 week</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        This course is aimed at boys and girls who have developed a keen interest in food. A basic knowledge of cooking is required. Students cook at least 2 dishes both savoury and sweet, which they take home. Also suitable for students preparing for their Junior Cert practical. 🍲🧁
      </p>
      
      <a href="#contact" class="mt-6 w-full block text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-pink-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg">
        Book Now! 🚀
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Level 3 -->
  <div class="fun-card border-4 border-purple-400 border-opacity-30 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-purple-50 relative overflow-hidden group">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 text-8xl opacity-10 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-500">
      ✨
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3 animate-bounce-slow">✨</div>
      
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
        Level 3
      </h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-2xl">⏰</span>
          <span class="font-semibold">3 Hours per day</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-2xl">💰</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-orange-500 text-xl">€215 for 1 week</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        Aimed at young boys and girls who have completed 2 years of Home Economics or Level 2. It's a very busy morning and it's important that students have all the basic skills. Students will supply their own ingredients. 🍕🎂
      </p>
      
      <a href="#contact" class="mt-6 w-full block text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-pink-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg">
        Book Now! 🚀
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Level 4 -->
  <div class="fun-card border-4 border-orange-400 border-opacity-30 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-orange-50 relative overflow-hidden group">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 text-8xl opacity-10 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-500">
      💫
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3 animate-bounce-slow">💫</div>
      
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-red-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
        Level 4
      </h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-2xl">⏰</span>
          <span class="font-semibold">3 Hours per day</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-2xl">💰</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-orange-500 text-xl">€215 for 1 week</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        This advanced level course is aimed at boys and girls who have completed 3 years of Home Economics or Level 3. Perfect for experienced young chefs ready to master complex dishes! 👨‍🍳🍰
      </p>
      
      <a href="#contact" class="mt-6 w-full block text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-pink-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg">
        Book Now! 🚀
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Preparatory Course -->
  <div class="fun-card border-4 border-green-400 border-opacity-30 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-green-50 relative overflow-hidden group">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 text-8xl opacity-10 group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-500">
      🎨
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3 animate-bounce-slow">🎨</div>
      
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-teal-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
        Preparatory Course
      </h3>
      
      <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-2xl">⏰</span>
          <span class="font-semibold">2.5 hours per day</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-2xl">💰</span>
          <span class="font-bold text-orange-500 text-xl">€235 for 1 week</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
        Aimed at young boys and girls. Students learn how to weigh and measure. Each student cooks and bakes 2 dishes which they take home. The importance of wholesome foods & healthy eating is emphasised. Ingredients provided! 🍪🥕
      </p>
      
      <a href="#contact" class="mt-6 w-full block text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-pink-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg">
        Book Now! 🚀
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mt-12 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);">
  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-white">
    <span class="text-4xl">🌈</span>
    Special Dietary Requirements
  </h3>
  <p class="text-lg text-white">
    We cater for all special dietary requirements including gluten free, wheat free, and lactose intolerant. 
    Feel free to contact us for more information! 💚
  </p>
</div>
